The Herald Blessings Chidakwa Municipal Reporter Zimbabwe United Passengers Company (Zupco) has introduced a convenient platform which allows one to buy tickets and book seats online through a partnership with Vaya. The concept termed ‘Vaya neZupco’ will see passengers now paying for their bus fares via web and mobile platforms like Ecocash. Speaking during the launch this Wednesday morning, Zupco acting chief executive Mr Evaristo Madangwa said this marks a great improvement in the way the mass public transporter operates.